===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
Originally a {{liushu|p|nocap=y}} – the sun ({{zh-l|*日}}) surrounded by lines on all sides – halo.

Now {{Han compound|日|軍|ls=psc|c1=s|c2=p|t1=Sun|nocap=y}}.

===Etymology===
Same word as {{och-l|運|to revolve; to move}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). See there for more.

